library(ggplot2)
library(tidyr)

Add a new chunk by clicking the Insert Chunk button on the toolbar or by pressing Cmd+Option+I.

df <- read_csv('datasets assignment 2/Spotify-2000.csv') %>%
  select(c('Danceability',
            'Beats Per Minute (BPM)',
            'Energy',
            'Liveness',
            'Valence',
            'Speechiness',
            'Acousticness' )) %>%
  na.omit()
